:<!--Trigger PerformanceE 200010111: Config/Level/Mission/2000101/Act/Act200010111.json-->
:'''Hinkel:''' ...What is this? "Battle of intellects is a source of pride. Physical exertion brings shame"? It's complete nonsense! So physical labor doesn't count as work now?
:'''Hinkel:''' Today, I'm gonna show them all what real work is about!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Yep, show them!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Hear! Hear!
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200022303-->
:'''Hinkel:''' All staff present, attention please &mdash; Herta Space Station is undergoing a difficult period of revival.
:'''Hinkel:''' In the battle with the Legion, some of our colleagues were slaughtered by monsters, and their cold bodies were thrown into the silent space.
:'''Hinkel:''' The cyber attack has erased years of research efforts. The damaged Curios are slowly disintegrating in a weightless environment.
:'''Hinkel:''' Everything within sight has been turned into a wasteland, and monsters are still roaming around in our cabins.
:'''Hinkel:''' No matter how many dazzling achievements you have made on your own, we can no longer afford to live like hermits.
:'''Hinkel:''' We need to mobilize every member of our staff, put down our inherent prejudices, and work together to recover the lost Curios and repair the damaged cabins.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} So inspiring!
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200022312-->
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} So lame...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200022313-->
::'''Hinkel:''' Silence! If any staff member feels unhappy with this, please air your grievances to me face to face.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm all ears.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200022312-->
:'''Hinkel:''' If you don't mind, I don't want to hear any more complaints about physical labor, nor do I want to see anyone putting off work.
:'''Hinkel:''' If you are interested in Curio recovery, please report to the Curio Collection Squad under Mr. Wen Mingde in the base zone as soon as possible.
:'''Hinkel:''' Those who are interested in repair work, come to me now to learn the process.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I can help with the repairs.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200022319-->
::'''Hinkel:''' Good, good. Are you the young {{MC|m=man|f=lady}} who helped out in the master control zone? I have a special task for you.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Does everyone have to participate?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200022321-->
::'''Hinkel:''' Every staff member must take responsibility sooner or later. The space station is now in dire need of restoration. I believe we can use everyone's help.
::'''Hinkel:''' I remember you. You are the young {{MC|m=man|f=lady}} who helped out in the master control zone. Great. I have a special task for you.
:'''Hinkel:''' 45 meters out the door from where we are now, there is a major road defect.
:'''Hinkel:''' I've checked, and the small ordnance depot on the other side of the defect is swarming with monsters. I'm afraid ordinary staff won't be able to deal with this.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Don't worry. Just leave it to me.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Looks like I am the only one...
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200022326-->
:'''Hinkel:''' Yes, {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|make sure to repair the road and eliminate the monsters at the end of it.}}
:'''Hinkel:''' I have many other matters to attend to. Please report back to me when you finish the task.
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Mission_200010111-->
